# On elja the file's path is /hpchome/ubf2/Homo_sapiens.GRCh37.65.gtf.gz
# Use gunzip Homo_sapiens.GRCh37.65.gtf.gz to get Homo_sapiens.GRCh37.65.gtf

# To get gene names for convenience I used /hpchome/ubf2/The-Epigenetic-Machinery.csv I have stored on elja but
# this file can be downloaded as a csv file from https://www.epigeneticmachinery.org/ (button at the top of the site)

